  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "7. Uppuri un Ehdamo-Uppu-\nri tew ne patikke/ tu eſt man\ntaſs Aufis tsurbis/ Dedsaimo-\nUppurus un Grehku-Uppurus tu\nne eſti praſſijs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "8. Tad fazzijn eg: Raugi/es\nnahku/ Grahmata̅ stahw ne\nmannim rakſtihts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "9. Man irr labs Prahts ta-\nwu labbu Prahtu/mans Deews/\npadarricht/ un tawa Kaſſiba\nirr mannâ Sirde Dibbinâ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "10. Es fluddingſcht to Tait-\nnibu eekſch tahs leelas Draudſes/\nrangi/ es ne liſſchohs fawu Mut-\nti aisbahst/ KUNGS tu finni to.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "11. Tawu Taifnibu es ne\nflepjn mannâ Sirđi/ no tawas\nPateefibas un Peſtitchanas run-\nnaju es/ tawu Scheblastibu un\nPeetizzibu es ne apflepju eekſch\ntahs leelas Draudſes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "12. Tu al KUNGS! ne no-\nwehrſ tawu Upschehloſchanu no\nmannim/ lai tawu Scheblastiba\nun Pateefiba weenuuehr man-\nni pafarga.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "13. Jo apkahrt mann irr\nBehdas mettuſchees/ ko ſkaitiht\nne warr/ manni Noseegumi irr\nmanni fagrabbuschi/ ka es re-\ndseht ne warru/ winnu irr wai-\nraſ/ ne fa Matti us mannu\nalwu/ un manna Sirds irr\nin atſtahjusi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "14. Leezeeß few pat\nKUNGS/ mann iſglahbt/\ndseeß af KUNGS! man\nPaligu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "15. Lai Kannâ tohp un\npa par Smeekli ktuhſt/ kas m\nnu Dwehteli mekle/ winnu\nmaitaht/ lai tohp atpakkat d\nun Kannâ lieti/ kam manna\nlatuiba patihk.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "16. Lai tee ſawas Beſka\nbas deht iſtrubzinajahs/ kaē\nmannim faſka: Ta/ ta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "17. Laid preezajahs un li\nmojahs eekſch tewim/ wiſſt/\ntewis mekle/ un lai tee/ kas\nwu Peſtitchanu mihto/ allaf\nfaſka: Tas KUNGS irr a\nfit teizains.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "18. Gann es eſmu behd\nun nabbags/ bet tas KUNG\ngahda par manni/ tu eſt m\nPaligs un mans Iſglahbejs/\nmans Deews! ne kawejees.\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
